item.name: comp Name of the current JIT compiler
comp Accumulated time spent in compilation
gc PS MarkSweep number of collections per second
gc PS MarkSweep accumulated time spent in collection
gc PS Scavenge number of collections per second
gc PS Scavenge accumulated time spent in collection

item_prototype.name: TotalMessageCount per minute for {#JMXBROKERNAME}
item_prototype.description: Number of unacknowledged messages on the broker per minute

item_prototype.name: AverageEnqueueTime for {#JMXVALUE}
item_prototype.description: Average time a message has been held this destination

item_prototype.name: ConsumerCount for {#JMXVALUE}
item_prototype.description: Number of consumers subscribed to this destination.

item_prototype.name: DequeueCount per minute for {#JMXVALUE}
item_prototype.description: Number of messages per minute that have been acknowledged (and removed from) from the destination.

item_prototype.name: EnqueueCount per minute for {#JMXVALUE}
item_prototype.description: Number of messages per minute that have been sent to the destination.

item_prototype.name: ExpiredCount per minute for {#JMXVALUE}
item_prototype.description: Number of messages per minute that have been expired.

item_prototype.name: ProducerCount for {#JMXVALUE}
item_prototype.description: Number of producers publishing to this destination

item_prototype.name: QueueSize for {#JMXVALUE}
item_prototype.description: Number of messages in the destination which are yet to be consumed. Potentially dispatched but unacknowledged.

trigger.expression: {Template JMX ActiveMQ:jmx["java.lang:type=MemoryPool,name=PS Old Gen",Usage.used].last(0)}>({Template JMX ActiveMQ:jmx["java.lang:type=MemoryPool,name=PS Old Gen",Usage.max].last(0)}*0.7)
trigger.name: 70% mp PS Old Gen used on {HOST.NAME}
70% os Opened File Descriptor Count used on {HOST.NAME}
gc PS Mark Sweep in fire fighting mode on {HOST.NAME}
mem Heap Memory fully committed on {HOST.NAME}
mp Code Cache fully committed on {HOST.NAME}

trigger.expression: {Template JMX ActiveMQ:jmx["java.lang:type=MemoryPool,name=PS Old Gen",Usage.committed].last(0)}={Template JMX ActiveMQ:jmx["java.lang:type=MemoryPool,name=PS Old Gen",Usage.max].last(0)}
trigger.name: mp PS Old Gen fully committed on {HOST.NAME}
